{"tid":270364,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆想買機，有冇咩機抵玩?","createTime":"2017-06-04T09:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T16:19:32.000Z","uid":69625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"689687ca15de378c8d7c6a145e34d1b037335f37","tid":270364,"uid":69625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"本身老豆執緊我老母部LG G3手尾<br />\n近排好似SHORT SHORT地<br />\n用到佢成日惱羞成怒<br />\n之後佢話佢想換機<br />\n想知有咩機抵玩?<br />\n筆直大約4000樓下<br />\n佢要求既係想影相好(佢好撚鐘意影相...)<br />\n本身成撚日上YOUTUBE同睇戲<br />\n其他都唔係話太著重，佢亦都唔打機<br />\n所以唔洗話要太新款既旗艦機<br />\n但最好係大路既牌子(我推1+3比佢佢唔撚愛，小米佢都唔想用)<br />\n同佢出去睇下<br />\n佢對華為部P9 PLUS同新既P10都有少少興趣<br />\n但P10就有少少OVER左<br />\n巴絲有咩好介紹?<br />\n利申: 粗人一個所以1999，梳鳩RE"},{"pid":"eb5fdc7223e09e69e91904f76d1f9bf49eec7e81","tid":270364,"uid":63944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54751e9b99aae358196bf0a80e2bb8210fb3ced8","tid":270364,"uid":69625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>c7 pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSORRY<br />\n上面講漏左<br />\n佢對SAMSUNG有少少偏見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4719b89c10ed22c124bbe4100ce459f9c3d4cfce","tid":270364,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c965af93abf9efd34f50a60a3fa30a784bc9cbb","tid":270364,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:13:36.000Z","msg":"moto z play?"},{"pid":"6447c077e0e91c0395e8b80a9028f34c16a3c529","tid":270364,"uid":63944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9df2efa16ff29f4606a906509d3139775532a69a","tid":270364,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T1