r%2Fheadline%2F&d=0dU4zcMrQVK0%2BLeA1vlz3jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5276f219\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2011/03/19/internet-gunner/headline/</a><br />\n<br />\n「打手」成現今相當有效的推廣工具<br />\n<br />\n網絡世界觀已經在扭曲，在網絡上的產品評測稍有讚揚，網民便會不理因由地直斥你是「廣告」，網民大都會選擇相信一些所謂的「用家意見」，例如討論區的個人發表及 Blogger 分享等。有見及此，各品牌都全力向這兩方面進擊，網上打手就應運而生。簡單說打手的工作就是假裝成一般用家，為一些產品美言或護航，今次我們 <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=0dU4zcMrQVK0%2BLeA1vlz3jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4ff4cd5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> 請來網絡打手的「阿偉」爆料，讓大家更清楚網絡打手的工作"},{"pid":"40c3782a9cef08e780a9c537d2115a729ee5a698","tid":270364,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華為都睇得出眼<br />\n用紅米好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸機之中華為都算貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1c610f5568c3e36c7d4bb1ade8bf9c66be79b3","tid":270364,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"全部an機都係垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acd814053b2c6a1074d0ab37cb2c5c9806f4da1","tid":270364,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"iPhone 7"},{"pid":"6abd1faaf8ba4800b3a2bf344ab16350abae14b6","tid":270364,"uid":104952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb54b78df78be98013cffeffa6cf2ada76f4b566","tid":270364,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HTC 10/ U Ultra<br />\n<br />\n老人家換機無咁密    部機兩三年之後既表現好緊要<br />\n<br />\nsamsung d 機半年後就窒</blockquote><br />\n而家10仔3498<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}